'''天使女巫'''（{{lang-en|'''Angel Witch'''}}）是一支[[英国|英国]]重金属乐队，1977 年成立于[[伦敦|伦敦]]，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/angelwitchofficial/info|title=Facebook|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=}}</ref>成为'''[[英国重金属新浪潮|英国重金属新浪潮]]'''中的一员。

== 经历 ==
在乐队成立之初他们的名字叫 Lucifer<ref>{{Cite book|title=The NWOBHM Encyclopedia|last=|first=|publisher=|year=2001|isbn=9783931624163|location=|pages=}}</ref>，原始阵容为吉他手兼主唱 Kevin Heybourne<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Kevin_Heybourne/14485|title=Kevin Heybourne|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101022925/https://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Kevin_Heybourne/14485|dead-url=no}}</ref>，吉他手 Rob Downing<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Rob_Downing/14508|title=Rob Downing|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427133548/https://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Rob_Downing/14508|dead-url=no}}</ref>，鼓手 Steve Jones<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Steve_Jones/545979|title=Steve Jones|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426160204/https://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Steve_Jones/545979|dead-url=no}}</ref>，和贝斯手 Barry Clements。<ref>{{Cite book|title=New Wave of British Heavy Metal Vol 1|last=|first=|publisher=|year=1995|isbn=3931624005|location=|pages=}}</ref>后来乐队分裂，Steve Jones 加入到'''[[布鲁斯·迪金森|布鲁斯·迪金森]]'''的乐队 Speed 中<ref>{{Cite book|title=Iron Maiden: Run to the Hills, the Authorised Biography|last=|first=|publisher=|year=|isbn=1-86074-542-3|location=|pages=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Speed/16757|title=Speed|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423193837/https://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Speed/16757|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除 Barry Clements 外，Lucifer 余下的成员组成了 '''天使女巫'''（{{lang-en|'''Angel Witch'''}}）。并由 Kevin Riddles<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Kevin_%22Skids%22_Riddles/14521|title=Kevin "Skids" Riddles|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423211931/https://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Kevin_%22Skids%22_Riddles/14521|dead-url=no}}</ref> 取代 Barry Clements，Dave Hogg<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Dave_Hogg/14487|title=Dave Hogg|accessdate=2016-07-05|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424214445/https://www.metal-archives.com/artists/Dave_Hogg/14487|dead-url=no}}</ref> 取代 Steve Jones，次年 Rob Downing 离开队伍。

